  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support order fulfilment, picking, packing for accurate and timely delivery of goods</li>\n  <li>Support shipment loading &amp; unloading activities</li>\n  <li>Ensure shipments and inventory transactions accuracy</li>\n  <li>Organize and maintain inventory and storage area</li>\n  <li>Plan delivery routes and coordinate with internal and external customers on delivery</li>\n  <li>Work with various departments to resolve warehouse operation related issues</li>\n  <li>Ensure Workplace Safety procedure are fully compiled</li>\n  <li>Measure and report the effectiveness of warehousing activities and employees performance</li>\n  <li>Assist in data collection and reporting</li>\n  <li>Compile and update SOPs for the warehouse</li>\n  <li>Project manage process improvement initiatives and ensure project becomes sustainable and updated within business continuity plans</li>\n  <li>Any ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant area of study in the supply chain field and willingness to learn</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and energetic</li>\n  <li>Good team player with good interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, ERP experience is an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Forklift experience is an added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
